Thanks for using Fishing Points! To make our app better for you, we bring updates to the App Store regularly.

- Set anchor location, monitor your movements and get alerted if you exceed allowed distance
- You can use Sign-in with Apple for Backup & Restore
- All locations that have catches are marked with yellow ring on the map
- Now you can delete multiple locations at once by long pressing on the list
- Fixed rare crash during a Backup
- Fixed rare crashes when scrolling catch list
- Fixed disappearing settings
- When performing a Backup, screen stays on
- Use Backup & Restore feature to backup your Fishing Points data to the Cloud and restore it back when you change to a new device
- Improved performance when viewing catches
- various minor improvements and changes

Thanks for using Fishing Points! To make our app better for you, we bring updates to the App Store regularly.

Nautical maps are now available for the whole world! Know your depths, travel safely, fish smarter and catch more.

Other changes:
- Hourly weather expanded to wind gusts and precipitation intensity
- Weather: Tap on hourly precipitation chart to toggle between intensity and probability
- Weather: Fixed wind animation on certain devices
- Locations: Sharing a location as link supports icon
